room_title: Escape room "Island Escape" by Breakout Games - Des Moines in Des Moines
review: Eight of us tried this for an evening out. We did the Island Escape - we didn't solve it but had a great time. Definitely recommend this for a good adult night out.

room_title: Escape room "Island Escape" by Breakout Games - Des Moines in Des Moines
review: We had a great time doing team building together. We broke out of the Island Escape room in 51:02. Thanks, Aaron for being our game master.

room_title: Escape room "Island Escape" by Breakout Games - Des Moines in Des Moines
review: Our family of 5 (2 parents and 3 kids ages 7, 10, and 13) had a great time today in the Island Escape room! Steven was great and provided just the right amount of help when we needed it!

room_title: Escape room "Island Escape" by Breakout Games - Des Moines in Des Moines
review: We had so much fun! First time doing this and we also had friends in from Kentucky! They LOVED it. We did the Island Escape and it was perfect for all of us, we had 9 people and the youngest is 2 ! Next time we are going to try the kidnapping room
